{"tid":1007839,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【矛盾大對決】中共中央政法委員會宣傳短片公然抄襲Mario","createTime":"2019-02-04T05:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T15:17:15.000Z","uid":138409,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"69fc87b6922209b90f0b68d00eb5a126d809140c","tid":1007839,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T05:12:26.000Z","msg":"未打輸過官司嘅任天堂法務部 VS 睬你法律都有味嘅中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名等睇Mario成為中國品牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「致敬」呢家嘢你識條春咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/02/03/china-official-copied-mario-video/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR06zdJoWWqa2RQ98MbPIhFgqvw58mGXa_U-T2vSA2E1QNYe7HpJygeOpRE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F02%2F03%2Fchina-official-copied-mario-video%2Ffun-tech%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR06zdJoWWqa2RQ98MbPIhFgqvw58mGXa_U-T2vSA2E1QNYe7HpJygeOpRE&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToOm6EOSy25kVi46SvbSXLY8%3D&h=8ebe42ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/02/03/china-official-copied-mario-video/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR06zdJoWWqa2RQ98MbPIhFgqvw58mGXa_U-T2vSA2E1QNYe7HpJygeOpRE</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sgdn4S1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSgdn4S1.jpg&h=370260c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國的抄襲案例屢見不鮮，最近就連共產黨官方機構也公然抄襲任天堂的瑪莉奧遊戲畫面。最近委員會公開的反貪宣傳片，不僅片名直接提及 Super Mario 的名字，裏面的畫面更照抄瑪莉奧，令人側目。<br />\n<br />\n這個名為「Super Mario Mr. Judge 2018 湖南法院闖關記」的影片由中共中央政法委員會在官方新聞微博發佈，內容以超級瑪莉奧遊戲的方式介紹湖南法院去年打擊貪污犯罪活動的功績，主角瑪莉奧隨着熟悉的遊戲音樂，打倒途中出現的老虎和蒼蠅，估計是與習近平之前提過的「老虎、蒼蠅一起打」互相呼應，並收集「金融案件」、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「知識產權」</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、「醫療糾紛」等金幣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4sXHkrv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4sXHkrv.jpg&h=2b6b37a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於無論內容的<span style=\"color: gold;\">角色、畫面、音樂，甚至影片標題，都是直接抄襲任天堂的超級馬莉奧</span>，事件被日本媒體揭發後引起廣泛關注，而後來中共中央政法委員會亦已經移除影片。任天堂方面回應指不針對個別個案發表評論。"},{"pid":"bfa6c14f40740ed288ef640feeac9b6018da5392","tid":1007839,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T05:14:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0520eb08b1fc1ed4f5b15af3768ffd1fa2e43657","tid":1007839,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T05:16:37.000Z","msg":"就算政府有版權司法豁免都好<br />\n咁直抄只係證明私有財產喺中國不被保障"},{"pid":"e6abb9fb68830511278919c945fdde7ac5b1d327","tid":1007839,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T05:37:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9124a93e62f3be540da5456b6905611f507c8e20","tid":1007839,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T14:48:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d29bd8e0076d0e8dc7995047ba4d839794d37c80","tid":1007839,"uid":75767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T14:51:02.000Z","msg":"任天堂淆撚到 驚得罪大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d37be45f91d57c734f4e882f2d1e51e4a3d711","tid":1007839,"uid":64858,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"任天堂垃圾"},{"pid":"0058f6ad557f662bd4147df17f04c153d98ca486","tid":1007839,"uid":43225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T15:17:15.000Z","msg":"任天堂平時告人告到仆街<br />\n律師團隊業界最強"}]}